description: The WisdomTree Enhanced Commodity UCITS ETF – USD Acc (the “Fund”) seeks to track the performance, before fees and expenses of the Optimised Roll Commodity Total Return Index (the "Index").The Fund also aims to outperform the Bloomberg Commodity Index TR over the long term. The Fund invests in US Treasury Bills and uses total return swaps to deliver the Index performance. The swaps are collateralised on a daily basis and reset monthly.
name: WisdomTree Enhanced Commodity UCITS ETF USD Acc
